data.description: Check out the NEW INTERIOR PAINT! This charming home is so bright and cheery, just being there will make you happy! The location is perfect, the country feel you've been looking for, while still close to shopping and easy highway access. This home and lot are private and serene! The original wood floors and built ins are features you don't find in new construction! The living room is very spacious with beautiful windows that let in all the natural light, which highlights the amazing wood floors! The formal dining room has built in storage, a slider that walks out to a newly stained deck and fire pit! Don't miss the stunning chandelier! The kitchen has tons of storage and is so bright and cheery! The bedrooms are very spacious and have the most fabulous built in closets and storage! The original woodwork is breathtaking! The 3rd bedroom currently serves as the main floor laundry, but don't despair, there's another laundry hookup in the basement! This room can easily be converted back to a bedroom (the seller believes there are wood floors under the carpet). The basement is semi-finished and would be the perfect recreation room, media room, gym, additional primary suite...the options are endless!! If you still want more space, the attic is waiting on your finishing touches! There's so much room in this house, you might get lost! There's also ample outdoor space, the private, peaceful lot is approximately .79 acres, has a great storage shed, fire pit and a newly stained deck! You can sit on the deck and watch the deer, fox, and other wildlife! A great place to have morning coffee or a cold drink after a hard day! In addition to the 1 car attached garage, there's a car port behind the house! The house has so much charm and personality, you'll be smitten the moment you come through the front door!! Don't let this gem get away!
